commentTextItems.html: full and on the legs, Dighe takes a wild swipe and misses, that is the end of the game

commentPostTextItems.html: A good victory set up by some good batting and then quality fast bowling from Colleymore (4/49) saw West Indies through to victory
That brings us to the end of an exciting Coca-Cola Cup in Zimbabwe
West Indies are the deserving winners on the day
We hope you enjoyed watching the cricket with us, it was a pleasure bringing it to you. Mail all feedback to comms@cricinfo.com
Till the next time, a very good night to you all

stories.title: West Indies upset India in Coca-Cola Cup final
stories.summary:
In an upset result, West Indies overturned the form book to record a
16-run victory over India on Saturday to win the Coca-Cola Cup final
at the Harare Sports Club, after twice losing to the same opposition
in the preliminary round
